### 🚀 Featured Projects

#### 🤖 [AI-Powered Mock Interview Platform](https://github.com/chandu336949)
*A full-stack web application that simulates real-world technical interviews using generative AI.*
- **Tech Stack:** React.js, Node.js, Express, MongoDB, JWT, Gemini AI, AssemblyAI, Murf AI
- **Key Features:** Built a multi-step resume parsing wizard, integrated live audio transcription/speech synthesis streams, and embedded a custom Monaco Code Editor interface for live coding segments.

#### 🗺️ [Learning Path Generator via MCP](https://github.com/chandu336949)
*A modular web dashboard that automatically generates personalized educational syllabi based on custom timelines.*
- **Tech Stack:** Python, Streamlit, Model Context Protocol (MCP), Google AI Studio, Pipedream
- **Key Features:** Leveraged MCP to broker cross-platform resources and integrated webhooks to dynamically aggregate related YouTube lectures and documentation.

#### 🫁 [Pneumonia Detection Deep Learning CNN](https://github.com/chandu336949)
*An automated medical imaging pipeline to detect pneumonia from chest X-ray images.*
- **Tech Stack:** Python, TensorFlow, Keras, NumPy, Pandas, Matplotlib
- **Key Features:** Constructed a 2-layer CNN architecture with sequential feature scaling, attaining an **87% test accuracy threshold**.

